snippet.title: [MISTOVER] PAX EAST 2019 Recap
snippet.description:
MISTOVER made our first debut at PAX EAST 2019. Fans and press alike lined up to play it and Aimo team is glad to say that a lot of players really ENJOYED our game! Marooner’s Rock honored MISTOVER with a “Best of Show” for PAX EAST 2019. Please sit back and enjoy MISTOVER’s PAX EAST Recap!

Official site: https://www.playmistover.com/ 
Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/909510/MISTOVER/
Nintendo Switch eShop: To be Announced. 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MISTOVER_EN
